{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"tGlp6PEYoR1bjZhiuX057","title":"Doordash On-Demand Logistics","desc":"","updated":1644627662986,"created":1644627013359,"custom":{},"fname":"seed.Product Management.Case Studies.Doordash On-Demand Logistics","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"345567d5a8685c4ad6f1c92ba6f43b50","links":[],"anchors":{"dispatch-type-problems":{"type":"header","text":"Dispatch type problems","value":"dispatch-type-problems","line":15,"column":0,"depth":1},"steps":{"type":"header","text":"Steps","value":"steps","line":22,"column":0,"depth":1},"balance-supply-and-demand":{"type":"header","text":"Balance Supply and Demand","value":"balance-supply-and-demand","line":23,"column":0,"depth":2},"route-planning":{"type":"header","text":"Route Planning","value":"route-planning","line":25,"column":0,"depth":2},"matching":{"type":"header","text":"Matching","value":"matching","line":29,"column":0,"depth":2},"actions":{"type":"header","text":"Actions","value":"actions","line":39,"column":0,"depth":1},"core-matching-happens-on-the-fly":{"type":"header","text":"Core Matching happens on the fly.","value":"core-matching-happens-on-the-fly","line":42,"column":0,"depth":1}},"children":[],"parent":"ygF579NAkcnNw54IdeyVL","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"doordash-on-demand-logistics\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#doordash-on-demand-logistics\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Doordash On-Demand Logistics</h1>\n<p>3- sided marketplace</p>\n<p>Merchants, eaters, drivers.</p>\n<p>Eaters-drivers:\nBalance supply-demand, use levers, such as dynamic pricing (duh).</p>\n<h1 id=\"dispatch-type-problems\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#dispatch-type-problems\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Dispatch type problems</h1>\n<p>Core engine that powers fulfillment. Core assignment (match drivers to deliveries).</p>\n<p>High-level goal- fast and efficient deliveries. </p>\n<h1 id=\"steps\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#steps\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Steps</h1>\n<h2 id=\"balance-supply-and-demand\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#balance-supply-and-demand\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Balance Supply and Demand</h2>\n<h2 id=\"route-planning\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#route-planning\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Route Planning</h2>\n<h2 id=\"matching\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#matching\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Matching</h2>\n<p>So they first balance the marketplace in general, then decide on fulfillment routes, order batching, etc.\nThen assign route sets to drivers, basically...</p>\n<p>Is it real time. First, the supply-demand balance has a planning horizon of a week.</p>\n<p>Continue to update predictions as we go.</p>\n<h1 id=\"actions\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#actions\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Actions</h1>\n<p>Pricing, messaging to drivers, incentives (pricing).</p>\n<h1 id=\"core-matching-happens-on-the-fly\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#core-matching-happens-on-the-fly\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Core Matching happens on the fly.</h1>","noteIndex":{"id":"wn8PE1RhG0znK1alrGFYv","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1647507231129,"created":1631901573363,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"db285659ccac8b133c384de1ef51d